{"ID":"20250915173807-ie0edd7","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250915173807-ie0edd7","title":"车机熔丝的影响","type":"doc","updated":"20260330103705"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250915173812-3d28dy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915173812-3d28dy5","updated":"20250915173816"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"熔丝后，车机要求进行mbn文件签名：否则对应后端能力将无法使用，需要签名的列表如下"}]},{"ID":"20250915173812-d3wmx86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915173812-d3wmx86","updated":"20260330103705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20250915173821-xld4308.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20250915173828-74ukfh9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915173828-74ukfh9","updated":"20250915173828"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不影响应用的部分由斑马安全组进行操作即可。"}]},{"ID":"20250915173833-c32o5s4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250915173833-c32o5s4","updated":"20250915173833"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"影响应用部分，需要应用owner先把用到的so库，打包进使用的mbn中，如：补盲需要使用cdsp，就需要把so信息打包入cdsp.mbn文件中，再由安全组进行签名。"}]}]}